text: Ibrahim Awariki (22 January 1928 - 15 September 2002) was a Lebanese wrestler. He competed in the men's Greco-Roman lightweight at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1928 births Category:2002 deaths Category:Lebanese male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Lebanon Category:Wrestlers at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:People from Nabatieh
